      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty strong stance. Specifically, though, why do you say human intervention adds \"systemic discrimination\"? Most people would argue that a diverse group of humans is exactly what's needed to *prevent* discrimination in an automated system. Do you think those human reviewers would actually be less objective than you?",
